## 5. raw#10 honest C3

1. **sparsentan Filspari 2023 → 2024 FSGS** = first FDA dual endothelin A + angiotensin II type 1 receptor antagonist. IgAN 2023 + FSGS 2024 (DUPLEX trial expansion). 단일 small molecule 의 dual antagonism — quantum-VQE 의 dual pocket fit 직접.
2. **atrasentan Vanrafia 2025 + zibotentan research** = ETA selective expansion. ETA + AT1 dual (sparsentan) vs ETA only (atrasentan/zibotentan) selectivity 비교 = quantum-VQE fit.
3. **inaxaplin VX-147 research** = first APOL1-targeted small molecule. African ancestry FSGS high-risk genotype G1/G2 paradigm-shift. quantum-VQE 의 APOL1 pocket leverage.
4. **rituximab + obinutuzumab + inebilizumab anti-CD20/CD19 generation** = membranous (PLA2R+) + MCD steroid-sparing paradigm. cross-bone_marrow_failure (B-cell depletion mechanism shared).
5. **finerenone Kerendia 2021 + dapagliflozin/empagliflozin SGLT2i 2020+** = diabetic CKD + 비당뇨 CKD 표준. nephrotic syndrome 의 만성 progression 보조 (cross-chronic_kidney_disease_specific).
6. **abatacept B7-1 podocyte FSGS research** = Reiser/Mundel B7-1 podocyte hypothesis. 임상 phase 변동 — quantum-VQE 의 PPI scaffold fit.
7. **fresolimumab anti-TGF-β + bardoxolone nrf2** = fibrosis-axis. fresolimumab phase II 종료 + bardoxolone diabetic CKD 안전성 withdrawn — research-only. NS fibrosis remains unmet need.
8. **K-NS framework + 식약처 + 산정특례** = 한국 임상 framework. 소아 NS 산정특례 + 한국형 protocol KSPN registry.
9. **NPHS1 + NPHS2 inherited NS + APOL1 high-risk** = 만성 가족성 + 인종별 risk stratification. cross-inherited_adult + pediatric_rare 강결합.
10. **wet-lab + clinical RCT 없음** — quantum-only in-silico, NS 임상 의미 한정.

